{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"14":"Fasting (Kitab Al-Siyam)"},"section_detail":{"14":{"hadithnumber_first":2313,"hadithnumber_last":2476,"arabicnumber_first":2313,"arabicnumber_last":2476}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2355,"arabicnumber":2355,"text":"Rapporté par Salman ibn Amir رضي الله عنه : Le Prophète ﷺ a dit : « Quand l’un de vous jeûne, qu’il rompe son jeûne avec des dattes ; s’il n’en trouve pas, alors avec de l’eau, car l’eau purifie. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":14,"hadith":43}}]}